{"tid":2075311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1994年，有一個新香港，日本仔行得好前","createTime":"2020-06-22T18:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T22:20:43.000Z","uid":326526,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"123d6b9b1cca5d9216113f829d1a6ec64972c30a","tid":2075311,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T18:42:02.000Z","msg":"講緊嘅又係機動武鬥傳G高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新香港</span></span>係獨立參賽！同場有新英國，新中國。故事中，平起平坐，齊爭世界管治權，而香港更加係主辦國。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1b0kbF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1b0kbF.jpg&h=e937bb34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為1994年嘅作品，多謝日本仔帶畀我地依段FF史<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港揸Fit人 - 黃潤發<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/cl-why2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cup.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F04%2Fcl-why2.jpg&h=0bc37007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屬於香港人 - 盟主高達<br />\n<img src=\"https://67.media.tumblr.com/bddb5b73c3784f63bd28993798077565/tumblr_of1j7usCWE1v296kfo2_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F67.media.tumblr.com%2Fbddb5b73c3784f63bd28993798077565%2Ftumblr_of1j7usCWE1v296kfo2_500.jpg&h=9ee93c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港產片文化 - 東方不敗<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.likejapan.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/capture-20190308-185305.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.likejapan.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2Fcapture-20190308-185305.jpg&h=829b522e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同感爆燈 - 九龍高達<br />\n<img src=\"https://i441.photobucket.com/albums/qq139/shengzhe1/21gk/bclub2/074/10033254a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi441.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fqq139%2Fshengzhe1%2F21gk%2Fbclub2%2F074%2F10033254a.jpg&h=64462bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有幾多當年嘅小學雞或者老餅會估到有今時今日⋯未睇過嘅，一定要睇，係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">新香港</span></span>啊！！"},{"pid":"1afddbd0636cfcc7b952fff425ea9cf0afc2d0e9","tid":2075311,"uid":252862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T18:43:05.000Z","msg":"石破天驚拳"},{"pid":"f00847d05cc9e3c9fa2da5a9fb7f63cfe5ef8da2","tid":2075311,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:42:54.000Z","msg":"Z已經有新香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過比我女神科唔小心整爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a474569f8eb658151bebbb464c7f24635cbff95","tid":2075311,"uid":126382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:51:07.000Z","msg":"個Master Asia咩料<br />\n日本人 + 滿清打扮 + 武俠小說人物名<br />\n剩係中間果個夠仆街，唔知香港人係南方漢人，最仇恨滿清暴政 ?"},{"pid":"a0ca50793300c799dc823bdfc109bb386f2f21a9","tid":2075311,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a474569f8eb658151bebbb464c7f24635cbff95","tid":2075311,"uid":126382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:51:07.000Z","msg":"個Master Asia咩料<br />\n日本人 + 滿清打扮 + 武俠小說人物名<br />\n剩係中間果個夠仆街，唔知香港人係南方漢人，最仇恨滿清暴政 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:58:31.000Z","msg":"依家唔同講法<br />\n偽滿州國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e1c503a384dc27642d11b3fef51721a6d18fd3","tid":2075311,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f00847d05cc9e3c9fa2da5a9fb7f63cfe5ef8da2","tid":2075311,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:42:54.000Z","msg":"Z已經有新香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過比我女神科唔小心整爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T19:59:24.000Z","msg":"原來咁耐歷史<img src=\